    "description": "<strong>概述</strong><br>这是一个利用有限的单位攻克关卡的策略类游戏.<br>本游戏难度颇高,适合喜欢有限资源规划/解谜/策略类的游戏玩家.<br><br><strong>关卡</strong><br>世界采用半开放自由探索模式,每个地区的关卡都有独特的单位机制和奖励.<br>而每个关卡由若干战役和资源构成,你需要利用地图上有限的单位资源规划路线攻克关卡.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271900/extras/d4e4b9af7c9a2291dc9fed938a575aa4.avif?t=1762534475\" width=600 height=400 /></span><br><br><strong>兵种</strong><br>每种单位都有独特的机制,都有优缺点,擅于利用会节约更多的资源.<br>此外,单位间还能相互配合利用,用更低的代价换取更多的资源.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271900/extras/d9eebf6aeab29a167f0f1677dcbc3a0a.avif?t=1762534475\" width=600 height=82 /></span><br><br><strong>战斗</strong><br>使用动作类战斗机制,单位攻击带有精确的实体判定,硬直和击退.<br>微调站位改变进攻时机,是除了兵种的搭配克制以外,另一个影响战局的重要手段.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271900/extras/99a863ef0476c77ea93c998e6c2fc572.poster.avif?t=1762534475\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271900/extras/99a863ef0476c77ea93c998e6c2fc572.webm?t=1762534475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271900/extras/99a863ef0476c77ea93c998e6c2fc572.mp4?t=1762534475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>奖励</strong><br>每个关卡都有1个独特的装备,解锁的新装备和新单位,可以用在其他关卡中.<br>它们在合适的搭配下,会使你的战斗事半功倍.<br>而某些关卡中可能还包含一些隐藏的奖励,需要触发特定的条件才能获得.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271900/extras/a8f87b5cdff59796a4d628b706b4919a.avif?t=1762534475\" width=600 height=218 /></span><br><br><strong>挑战</strong><br>尝试用更少的资源攻略更多的战役会获得更高的分数.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271900/extras/0dd90e6e2c106f3bed262f894560ae20.avif?t=1762534475\" width=598 height=294 /></span><br><br>欢迎加入QQ交流群：<br>测试群：721466795",
